Key Match Events: Ja Morant successfully executed a 360-degree mid-air spin to score a basket
Despite Morant's performance, the Memphis Grizzlies lost 106-104 to the Brooklyn Nets
Others: Ja Morant scored 25 points, nine rebounds, and five assists in the match
Dennis Schroder and Cam Johnson led the Nets with 20 points each
Zach Edey had a field day with 25 points and 12 rebounds for the Grizzlies
Jaren Jackson Jr. had 15 points for the Grizzlies
Dorian Finney-Smith and Cam Thomas chipped in with 17 and 13 points respectively for the Nets
